{"tid":1219170,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再稱呼佢哋係建制派","createTime":"2019-06-13T18:12:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T18:12:30.000Z","uid":260806,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"32adbf9f0e98b0233eef02a9955b7b5ecccb0467","tid":1219170,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:12:30.000Z","msg":"爲咗跟住落來嘅輿論戰，<br />\n從今日開始對建制派嘅稱呼要更正爲「親共派」、「親中派」或者「親北京派」。<br />\n可能「共狗」會更加適合，但係改成媒體會用嘅詞彙好啲。<br />\n從自己開始講，講到香港傳媒改爲止。<br />\n<br />\n例如 BBC 嘅報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-48619305?ocid=socialflow_facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR34cgrlif1gHVLWr3KvITM0lMDmDyClyPVnlr67cpEp__XP3_jrXsZbbvU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-48619305%3Focid%3Dsocialflow_facebook%26fbclid%3DIwAR34cgrlif1gHVLWr3KvITM0lMDmDyClyPVnlr67cpEp__XP3_jrXsZbbvU&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=f16de396\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-48619305%3Focid%3Dsocialflow_facebook%26fbclid%3DIwAR34cgrlif1gHVLWr3KvITM0lMDmDyClyPVnlr67cpEp__XP3_jrXsZbbvU&h=74c79b00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-48619305?ocid=socialflow_facebook&amp;fbclid=IwAR34cgrlif1gHVLWr3KvITM0lMDmDyClyPVnlr67cpEp__XP3_jrXsZbbvU</a><br />\n已經直接稱呼係「親北京派」。"}]}